properties.name: clean.indexes
properties.description: List of elasticsearch indexes to be cleaned by default all.

properties.name: clean.indexes-keep-days
properties.description: Days to retain data on indexes by default 365 days.

properties.name: clean.every-days
properties.description: Days to run the cleaner by default every 1 day.

properties.name: clean.at-hour
properties.description: Start hour to run the cleaner by default at 0 hours.

properties.name: clean.at-minute
properties.description: Start minutes to run the cleaner by default at 0 minutes.

properties.name: encrypt.secret-key
properties.description: A 128 bit secret key for encryptation.

properties.name: encrypt.indexes
properties.description: List of elasticsearch indexes to be encrypted by default ccaa_events.

properties.name: encrypt.attributes
properties.description: List of attributes to be encrypted by default identification, person, licensePlate, cardCode and description.

properties.name: encrypt.ignore-days
properties.description: Days to not encrypt data on indexes by default 30 days.

properties.name: encrypt.every-days
properties.description: Days to run the encryptation process by default every 1 day.

properties.name: encrypt.at-hour
properties.description: Start hour to run the encryptation process by default at 0 hours.

properties.name: encrypt.at-minute
properties.description: Start minutes to run the encryptation process by default at 0 minutes.
